1.1
log
@Do not break output lines in .Fn function arguments in SYNOPSIS mode.
Following an idea from Franco Fichtner, but implemented more cleanly.
This reduces groff-mandoc-differences in base by a fantastic 7.5%.
@
text
@d1 1
a1 1
.Dd December 25, 2013
d8 1
d11 11
d23 2
d26 13
@

